oposed models were consistently away more accurate than the previously\npresented GCRF model for multiscale networks [Jesse Glass and Zoran Obradovic.\nStructured regression on multiscale networks. IEEE Intelligent Systems,\n32(2):23-30, 2017.].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Sep 2019 20:11:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
