agnostics, and an array of precision detectors optimised to\nmeasure electrons, positrons and photons. Physics sensitivity projections based\non simulations are also provided.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Sep 2019 20:41:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
