onger\ndetectable at large separations, our result is consistent with a picture in\nwhich a significant fraction of quasars is triggered by mergers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Sep 2019 06:16:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-09"}
