on of our\nresult with the GHK equation is provided. The dual problem of reversal\npermanent charges is briefly discussed too.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Sep 2019 14:05:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Sep 2020 01:46:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-22"}
