 natural language to database querying has been carried\nout for SQL, and NoSQL share 15%, 10% and 5% of languages like SPAROL, CYPHER\nand GREMLIN respectively. It has also been observed that most of the frameworks\nsupport English language only.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Sep 2019 15:49:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-05"}
